**Bomb** | Attribute
__Basics__
The attribute of the Bomber. Bombed players will explode at the end of the night, killing all visitors.

__Formalized__
On Visited: Apply `Explosion` to @Visitor (~Phase) [@ThisAttr->Counter is 0]
Passive End Night: Attack @Self [@ThisAttr->Counter is 0]
Passive End Night: Increment Counter for @ThisAttr
